Scan markdown for :: markers

Usage: indiana <COMMAND>

Commands:
  serve      Run the daemon: bind the socket and hold the index in memory
  scan       Walk markdown and list every marker. With no path, asks a running daemon
  add        Add a folder to the monitored-folders config
  remove     Remove a folder from the monitored-folders config
  status     Show the daemon's monitored folders and marker counts
  copy       Compile markers and copy the bundle to the clipboard
  mcp        Run the MCP stdio server
  templates  Manage repo-local `.indiana` command templates
  service    Manage the launchd service
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

  -V, --version
          Print version

Kinds (for --kind):
  question     q, ?
  hate         h
  love         l
  keep         k
  fix          f
  elaborate    e
  note         n
  action       a
  todo         td
